sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant UI as Frontend Dashboard
  participant API as FastAPI /api/v1
  participant DB as ExecutionStore (SQLite)
  participant W as Execution Worker
  participant VR as ValuationRunner
  participant LG as LangGraphFinanceAgent
  participant SH as GoogleSheetsEngine
  participant MS as PostRunMemoService

  UI->>API: POST /executions {ticker}
  API->>DB: create_execution(status=QUEUED)
  API-->>UI: 202 ExecutionResponse

  loop Poll every 10s
    UI->>API: GET /executions?page=1&page_size=50
    API->>DB: list_executions()
    API-->>UI: items[] with status/timestamps/links
  end

  W->>DB: claim_next_queued() -> RUNNING
  W->>VR: run(ValuationRunRequest)
  VR->>LG: execute deterministic phases

  LG->>SH: copy template + prefill inputs
  LG->>SH: write_named_ranges/tables per phase allowlist
  LG->>SH: read_outputs(out_*)
  LG->>SH: finalize logs/citations/story hooks

  VR-->>W: ValuationRunResult(status=COMPLETED, spreadsheet_id)
  W->>MS: generate(with_memo=true)
  MS->>SH: read memo source ranges + sources table
  MS->>MS: render infographics + markdown/html/pdf + manifest

  alt Valuation + memo both complete
    W->>DB: mark_completed(company_name, sheet_url, memo_pdf_path)
  else Any failure
    W->>DB: mark_failed(error_message, partial artifacts)
  end

  UI->>API: GET /executions/{id}/memo.pdf
  API->>DB: load execution row
  API-->>UI: application/pdf (if path allowed and file exists)
